.TH "nvme_init_identify_nvmset_list" 9 "nvme_init_identify_nvmset_list" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_identify_nvmset_list \- Initialize passthru command for NVM Set List data structure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_identify_nvmset_list
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "__u16 nvmsetid "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_id_nvmset_list *nvmset "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Command data structure to initialize
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace identifier
.IP "nvmsetid" 12
NVM Set Identifier
.IP "nvmset" 12
User space destination address to transfer the data
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Identify command with
CNS value NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_NS_ACTIVE_LIST.
